Rating: 3
I make these regularly for my husband and boys, who love them right out of the oven, or as a quick carry-out morning snack. I love the fact that I can make them fresh, a few at a time -- in fact, they seem to raise more once the batter's been in the refrigerator a few days! Works with low-fat cream cheese; sprayed muffin tins with Pam and they come out fine.

